messages.message:
@Heymian and I synced offline:
> if we’re checking the flag for require MFA on the account setting page
As mentioned above, the env var `SITE_SETTINGS_REQUIRE_MFA` is only used in the sign up flow for aihub. If the env var is set, all users are forced to set up their MFA, which should not be the case rn. In the UI, users can still set up their MFA in the account settings page, if they wish
